<br>
the only other issue i might have would be snare, it being on the list of mage no no's that sony always had (remember the root earring that stopped dropping because it had mage as a usable class?) one way to work around that would be to make the pets spells bound to the pet itself, so when it dies, whatever it may have cast on the mob dies with it.<br>
